<p style="padding:5px 0;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;margin:0"><strong>Happy pre-TGIF. <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/2600.png" alt="☀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></strong></p>
